                            <comment id="252719" author="adilger" created="Thu, 8 Aug 2019 05:25:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would also be useful to add a &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs mirror flags {&amp;#45;&amp;#45;comp&amp;#45;id=N|--pool} &amp;#45;&amp;#45;comp&amp;#45;flags={prefer,nosync} &amp;lt;file&amp;gt; ...&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; command to set the flags on a specific mirror, which is the same as the &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lfs setstripe &amp;#45;&amp;#45;comp&amp;#45;flags&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; command that already exists, but is not easily found.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
